# UI
- Tailwind + shadcn/ui primitives from `src/shared/ui/`. Reuse before adding.
- Mobile-first and responsive. Support dark and light mode via theme tokens (no hard-coded colors).
- Accessible by default: semantic HTML, keyboard navigable, ARIA labels, sufficient contrast (WCAG).
- Minimal, purposeful animation only. Optimize images; lazy-load below the fold.
- Bilingual: Albanian (sq, primary) + English (en). No hard-coded user-facing strings — use i18n.
- Prefer Server Components; add `"use client"` only when interactivity requires it.
